channel.title: My Appliance
channel.description:
hey all. i'm not sure what the point of srl members is here, but hey i may as well apply ;)
you may have seen me at srl...my name is The Claw there as well and im an srl dev.
[b]Why you will be benificial to us as an SRL Member.[/b] I'm a pretty good scripter I reckon, not the best but not too bad either :P I'm not really that active here though, but I am at SRL. So dunno how much I can contribute here.
[b]Scripts that you have made.[/b] Auto kebab buyer (first script, hardly completes 1 load), Varrock West Miner, Any-fish power fisher, Lumbridge swamp miner, and Crafting guild miner. All were released apart from crafting guild miner, which is going to be part of a bigger project.
[b]Other scripting languages you know (If any).[/b] HTML, Javascript, a little php, VB.
[b]Example of a script you have made please.[/b] My LSM - http://www.srl-forums.com/forum/srl-4-lumbridge-t18553.html
